---
title: Sweet Soy Pork & Asian Veggie Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice
description: Say hello to your new dinner favourite! Tender pork mince gets a savoury oyster sauce glaze, bringing bold umami flavours to every bite. Paired with vibrant green veggies and fluffy jasmine rice, this dish is a perfect balance of savoury, fresh and comforting.
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
